## 5. Scope produk

### 5.1 In scope

| Modul | ID | Deskripsi singkat |
|-------|-----|-------------------|
| Dashboard | M0 | Daftar project BOM, CRUD, import Excel |
| Produk | M1 | Identitas, dimensi, kayu, coating |
| Struktur | M2 | Hierarki MODUL/SUBMODUL/PART, visual graph |
| Container | M3 | Packing, routing packing, kapasitas kontainer |
| Material | M4 | Kebutuhan material per PART |
| Proses | M5 | Rekap & detail operasi manufaktur |
| Summary | M6 | Kalkulasi per part + operasi nested |
| COGS | M7 | Waterfall biaya + markup + parity |
| FOB Jurnal | M8 | Baris journal ERP-style (custom lines) |
| Master Data | M9 | Mirror DATA BASE, ratio, coating, FOB, WC |
| Engine | M10 | Formula, rounding, biaya master, FOB cost |

### 5.2 Out of scope (v1.x)

- Modul ERP: Approval, QC Packing, Knife, Raw Ticket
- PLM / CAD sync
- MRP / work order execution
- Multi-company / multi-plant
- Mobile native app

### 5.3 Asumsi

- User memiliki akses master ERP (staging → production)
- Workbook Excel mengikuti template Spartan (sheet standar)
- Kurs USD/EUR di-set di header app (default 16004 / 17500)

### 5.4 Constraint

- Browser modern (Chrome/Edge); offline hanya mode dev seed
- Parity ketat (≤1,5%) prioritas produk curated (ZAN, FNA) dulu

