## 8. Master data & engine kalkulasi

### 8.1 Section DATA BASE (Excel → app)

| Section Excel | Unit umum | Picker |
|---------------|-----------|--------|
| WOOD | m³ | WoodGradeField |
| PLYWOOD, MDF, CORE, HPL, VENEER, EDGING | m³ / m² | DatabaseMaterialField |
| ASSEMBLING / FITTING HARDWARE | pcs, lbr, … | DatabaseMaterialField |
| TYPE OF VENEER, SANDING, FINISHING, PACKING | varies | DatabaseMaterialField |
| FOB COST | Rp/m³ per kontainer | COGS toggle |

### 8.2 Engine rules

| Engine | Input | Output |
|--------|-------|--------|
| `computeMaterialBiayaFromMaster` | masterId, qty, vol, unit | biaya, SF, WF |
| `computeCogs` | bom tree, packing, config | productionCost, totalCogs, sellingPrice |
| `computeFobExportCost` | container type, volume m³ | FOB Rp |
| `evalFormula` | FORMULA DATA registry | line costs |
| `roundingEngine` | ROUND COMPONENT | selling price rounded |
| `excelParityAudit` | project + mirror | score %, pass/fail items |

