| Fase | Sumber master | Catatan |
|------|---------------|---------|
| T0 (now) | Seed JSON + IndexedDB | Dummy/demo |
| T1 | Hybrid ERP + seed fallback | Pilot production |
| T2 | ERP API primary | Target go-live |

