## 9. User experience & alur kerja

### 9.1 Alur utama — buat BOM dari nol

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  A[Dashboard: Buat Baru] --> B[Isi Product Panel]
  B --> C[Tab Struktur: bangun tree]
  C --> D[Pilih material DATA BASE per PART]
  D --> E[Atur routing / proses]
  E --> F[Tab Container: packing]
  F --> G[Tab COGS: review waterfall]
  G --> H{Parity OK?}
  H -->|Ya| I[Export xlsx/PDF]
  H -->|Tidak| C
```

### 9.2 Alur alternatif — import Excel

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  I[Import xlsx] --> P[Parse sheets]
  P --> E[Editor terisi]
  E --> V[Parity checklist]
  V --> A[Adjust manual]
```

### 9.3 Prinsip UX

| Prinsip | Implementasi |
|---------|--------------|
| **Excel-first mental model** | 7 tab map ke sheet/workflow Excel |
| **Master-driven pricing** | Pilih SKU → harga & nama terisi |
| **Non-blocking navigation** | Tab bebas, tidak wizard paksa |
| **Visual hierarchy** | Graph + sticky columns struktur |
| **Auditability** | Parity score, colored nominal, export mirror |
| **Progressive disclosure** | Product panel collapse; FAQ modal |

### 9.4 Mode panduan (optional, parity ERP)

Overlay wizard 4 langkah untuk user migrasi dari ERPKu:
1. Produk Akhir → 2. Komponen → 3. Bahan Baku → 4. Operasi

