## 10. User stories & acceptance criteria

### Epic E1 — Project lifecycle

| Story | Acceptance criteria |
|-------|---------------------|
| **US-E1-01** Buat project kosong | Root MODUL, productInfo empty, COGS = 0, save IndexedDB |
| **US-E1-02** Import Excel | BOM TEMPLATE + SUMMARY mirror; buka editor < 5 menit |
| **US-E1-03** Auto-save | Debounce save; indikator Tersimpan/Menyimpan |

### Epic E2 — Struktur & material

| Story | Acceptance criteria |
|-------|---------------------|
| **US-E2-01** Tambah PART di SUBMODUL | Child muncul; tipe PART wajib materialType untuk picker |
| **US-E2-02** Pilih SKU DATA BASE | nama, kode, biaya terisi; kolom tipe hanya kategori |
| **US-E2-03** Search 800+ SKU | SearchableSelect filter < 300ms perceived |

### Epic E3 — Costing

| Story | Acceptance criteria |
|-------|---------------------|
| **US-E3-01** COGS waterfall | Setiap step running total benar vs manual Excel |
| **US-E3-02** Parity ZAN | totalCogs within 1,5% atau Rp 25.000 |
| **US-E3-03** FOB optional | COGS naik hanya jika checkbox aktif |
| **US-E3-04** Markup selling | ROUNDDOWN ribuan selaras ROUND COMPONENT |

### Epic E4 — Integrasi ERP (planned)

| Story | Acceptance criteria |
|-------|---------------------|
| **US-E4-01** Picker material ERP | API list materials; harga = ERP supplier price |
| **US-E4-02** Save draft ERP | POST project; status draft di ERP list |
| **US-E4-03** SSO login | Same session ERP staging |

### Epic E5 — Export

| Story | Acceptance criteria |
|-------|---------------------|
| **US-E5-01** Export Excel | Sheets: Struktur, Material, Proses, COGS, Summary |
| **US-E5-02** Export PDF lengkap | COGS + summary untuk review sales |

