## 11. Requirement non-fungsional

| Kategori | Requirement |
|----------|-------------|
| **Performance** | Editor 500 node tree usable; picker search ≤ 120 items visible batch |
| **Availability** | SPA offline after load (master cached); ERP mode needs network |
| **Security** | No credentials in repo; auth via ERP SSO (target) |
| **Compatibility** | Chrome/Edge latest; desktop 1440px+ recommended |
| **Maintainability** | `npm test` regression; modular engine vs UI |
| **Localization** | UI Bahasa Indonesia; format IDR `id-ID` |
| **Data integrity** | `schemaVersion` on project; normalize on load |
| **Auditability** | `excelMirror`, `importedFromExcel`, parity checklist export |

