## 16. Glosarium

| Istilah | Definisi |
|---------|----------|
| **BOM** | Bill of Materials — daftar komponen & proses produk |
| **COGS** | Cost of Goods Sold — total biaya pokok penjualan |
| **DATA BASE** | Sheet master SKU + harga di Excel |
| **MODUL / PART** | Level hierarki struktur BOM |
| **SF / WF** | Safety factor / Waste factor (%) |
| **FOB** | Free On Board — biaya export kontainer |
