## 18. Improvement Design — Flow & Tabel

> **Scope bagian ini:** perubahan UX modul BOM **di dalam ERPKu** — bukan app terpisah. Fokus **alur kerja (flow)** dan **definisi kolom tabel** per layar.

### 18.1 Tujuan improvement

| ID | Tujuan |
|----|--------|
| IF-1 | Satu modul BOM ERP menggantikan Excel untuk costing tanpa kehilangan kolom ERP |
| IF-2 | Flow non-linear (tab) + opsi **Mode Panduan** 4 langkah untuk user lama |
| IF-3 | Setiap tabel punya spec kolom frozen (tidak berubah tanpa PRD update) |
| IF-4 | Kolom costing Excel (SF/WF, MAT/PROD/PROD/U FX) masuk tab yang relevan |
| IF-5 | Expand row list + 7 tab detail = preview cepat + edit dalam |

### 18.2 Flow — AS-IS (ERP today) vs TO-BE (target)

#### AS-IS — Flow ERP saat ini

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  L[List /manufacture/bill-of-materials] --> F{Filters}
  F --> N[BOM Baru]
  N --> S1[Step 1: Produk Akhir]
  S1 --> S2[Step 2: Komponen]
  S2 --> S3[Step 3: Sub Perakitan & Bahan Baku]
  S3 --> S4[Step 4: Operasi]
  S4 --> SAVE[Simpan / Buat]
  L --> EXP[Expand row → preview Components]
```

**Karakteristik AS-IS:**
- Linear — harus lewat step berurutan
- Material & operasi di step terpisah, **tanpa** rollup COGS
- Master di sidebar (`/purchasing/materials`, WC, routing)
- Tidak ada import Excel / export SUMMARY COST

#### TO-BE — Flow improvement (target ERP)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  L2[List BOM — kolom ERP + expand] --> ACT{BOM Baru / Buka / Import Excel}
  ACT --> ED[Editor BOM — shell ERP]
  ED --> PP[Panel Produk — always visible]
  ED --> TABS{Tab navigator}
  TABS --> T1[Struktur]
  TABS --> T2[Container]
  TABS --> T3[Material]
  TABS --> T4[Proses]
  TABS --> T5[Summary]
  TABS --> T6[COGS]
  TABS --> T7[FOB Jurnal]
  TABS --> GUIDE[Mode Panduan 4 step — optional overlay]
  T6 --> PUB{COGS valid?}
  PUB -->|Ya| APR[Submit → Approval ERP]
  PUB -->|Tidak| T1
  APR --> EXP2[Export xlsx / PDF]
```

**Aturan flow TO-BE:**

| Aturan | Deskripsi |
|--------|-----------|
| F-01 | Entry **hanya** dari menu Manufacture → Bill of Materials (sama URL) |
| F-02 | Tab bebas; urutan rekomendasi: Produk → Struktur → Material → Proses → Container → Summary → COGS |
| F-03 | **Mode Panduan** = overlay step 1–4 map ke tab (lihat §18.3) |
| F-04 | Import Excel = path alternatif; hasil langsung ke tab terisi |
| F-05 | Simpan draft otomatis; finalisasi trigger approval ERP |
| F-06 | Master picker **selalu** API ERP (materials, products, WC) — bukan seed lokal |

#### Mapping flow wizard → tab (Mode Panduan)

| Step ERP lama | Tab TO-BE | Aksi user |
|---------------|-----------|-----------|
| 1 Produk Akhir | Panel Produk + tab Struktur (root) | Isi identitas + dimensi |
| 2 Komponen | Tab Struktur | Add ITEM / 5 grup kolom |
| 3 Sub Perakitan & Bahan Baku | Tab Material | Review PART + SF/WF |
| 4 Operasi | Tab Proses | Routing + biaya |
| — (baru) | Tab Container | Packing + kontainer |
| — (baru) | Tab Summary | Validasi per part |
| — (baru) | Tab COGS | Waterfall + parity |
| — (baru) | Tab FOB Jurnal | Journal lines |

**Acceptance criteria flow:**
- [ ] User dapat selesaikan BOM tanpa Mode Panduan (power user)
- [ ] User ERP lama dapat selesaikan dengan Mode Panduan tanpa training tab
- [ ] Import Excel → semua tab terisi ≥80% field vs manual
- [ ] Waktu navigasi antar-tab < 200ms perceived

